longBusinessSummary: CTCBIO Inc. provides various pharmaceutical products in South Korea and internationally. It offers animal and human pharmaceuticals; feed additives and ingredients; and functional food products. The company was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Seoul, South Korea.
